					<h2>Why build img<em>rszr</em>?</h2>
					<p>I&rsquo;ve run into many instances whilst in the web world where clients don&rsquo;t have access to Photoshop, or anything similar, so they <strong>can&rsquo;t resize images easily, or at all</strong>. So, I wanted to build a super-simple app that does just that, and that&rsquo;s <strong>fun, sleek, and, most of all, fast</strong>. You can use JPEGs, PNGs, GIFs and TIFFs with this. <em>Enjoy!</em></p>
